Package com.experian.aperture.datastudio.sdk.testframework

Common package of Aperture data SDK test framework.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    StepTestBuilderInterface
    Common interface shared across by the test builder class.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ColumnUniqueNamer
    Based on the Data Studio class, this ensures that there are never any identically named columns, and adds a postfix number if there are.
    ConstantValidator
    A class for validating constant name.
    MemoryCache
    Simple in memory implementation of Cache that will be used by step under test.
    ProgressRecord
    Model representing the data captured when progress was reported by the custom step.
    SDKAssertion
    The standard assertion class to verify the result of custom step execution.
    SDKAsyncAssertion
    Use together with SDKAssertion.
    SimpleLang
    Simplified version of DataX Lang.
    StepConfigurationTestBuilder
    Builder class specific to the configuration of the custom step.
    StepPropertyValueValidator
    A class for validating step property value.
    StepTestBuilder
    Builder to build a new custom step test session.
    StepTestJarBuilder
    Builder class for custom step that is loaded from a jar file.
    TestSession
    The test session that target a specific custom step.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ErrorMessages
    Defines error message when validating the custom steps.
    Parameter
    Common constant parameter class for SDK test framework.
    SimpleServerProperty
    Simplified version of com.experian.properties.ServerProperty.
